reviews.text: One of the most authentic Thai restaurant in HK island. Price is good for the food quality and environment that you get. Staff is super friendly and helpful. Highly recommend
Super authentic Thai kitchen. Really enjoyed the food and service. Thanks a lot. Even our baby liked being here ;-)
We tried the signature chicken and fish. The food is simply awesome. You can feel the love and passion. I definitely would come back again!
Food are dedicated made by this small cosy Thai restaurant. The service is great too. The only thing is a little overpriced.

Quite a small neighbourhood Thai restaurant with really friendly staff. 
The desserts are particularly good here - coconut icecream was excellent and the banana pancake is really good.
Well worth coming here.
